# Course staff

Teaching in the course is **interdisciplinary:**
 - Pharmacists delivering interactive lecture content (4 x pharmacists)
 - Pharmacist + Nurse/Midwife teaching workshops

<!--
header: PHRM7203 | MNSt ANMAC Re-accreditation
footer: ![height:0.5in](./figs/UQlogo.jpeg) 
-->

# Assessment

 - Workshop case presentation (1 per workshop) - 3 x 5% (15% total)
 - Case reflection video presentation - 35%
 - Written exam (MCQ and SAQ) - 50%



# Useful resources

- The Australian Medicines Handbook

- MIMS

- Therapeutic Guidelines

> Search **"UQ Pharmacy Library"** into google for all of these in one place

